| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1258 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 49958cdd-9347-54f6-a0d8-1e9d508e60c8"
